lyrics.text:
Lift up your heart,
lift up your voice; rejoice;
again I say, rejoice.

Lift up your heart,
lift up your voice; rejoice;
again I say, rejoice.

His kingdom cannot fail;
he rules o'er earth and heaven;
the keys of earth and hell
are to our Jesus given.

Lift up your heart,
lift up your voice; rejoice;
again I say, rejoice.
